      <title>印度市场监管机构将测试部分股票的即时结算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/india-market-regulator-to-test-instant-settlement-in-some-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度证券监管机构周五批准对 25 只股票试行其拟定的当日结算方案，试图吸引那些放弃直接押注股票、转而青睐更复杂衍生产品的散户投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/india-market-regulator-to-test-instant-settlement-in-some-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 17:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
