    <item>
      <title>由于交易员将美联储降息押注推迟至 7 月，美国国债暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/treasuries-slump-as-traders-push-fed-rate-cut-bets-out-to-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债下跌，十年期国债有望迎来今年最糟糕的一周，因为交易员越来越多地减少对美联储今年预期的货币宽松步伐和范围的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/treasuries-slump-as-traders-push-fed-rate-cut-bets-out-to-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管通胀上升，美联储仍将坚持 2024 年三度降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/fed-seen-sticking-with-three-2024-cuts-despite-higher-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社调查的经济学家表示，近期通胀上升不太可能改变美联储政策制定者今年降息 3 次、2025 年降息 4 次的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/fed-seen-sticking-with-three-2024-cuts-despite-higher-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
